SPostviewScreen_Result0=ROCK BOTTOM! I hope for your sake[CRLF]that you nuked that level.
SPostviewScreen_Result1=Better rethink your strategy before[CRLF]you try this level again!
SPostviewScreen_Result2=A little more practice on this level[CRLF]is definitely recommended.
SPostviewScreen_Result3=You got pretty close that time.[CRLF]Now try again for that few % extra.
SPostviewScreen_Result4=OH NO, So near and yet so far (teehee)[CRLF]Maybe this time.....
SPostviewScreen_Result5=RIGHT ON. You can't get much closer[CRLF]than that. Let's try the next...
SPostviewScreen_Result6=That level seemed no problem to you on[CRLF]that attempt. Onto the next....
SPostviewScreen_Result7=You totally stormed that level![CRLF]Let's see if you can storm the next...
SPostviewScreen_Result8=Superb! You rescued every lemmings on[CRLF]that level. Can you do it again....
SPostviewScreen_CongratulationOrig=[CRLF][CRLF]Congratulations![CRLF][CRLF][CRLF][CRLF][CRLF]Everybody here at DMA Design salutes you[CRLF]as a MASTER Lemmings player. Not many[CRLF]people will complete the Mayhem levels,[CRLF]you are definitely one of the elite[CRLF][CRLF][CRLF][CRLF][CRLF][CRLF]Now hold your breath for the data disk
SPostviewScreen_ResultOhNo0=Oh dear, not even one poor Lemming[CRLF]saved. Try a little harder next time.
SPostviewScreen_ResultOhNo1=Yes, well, err, erm, maybe that is[CRLF]NOT the way to do this level.
SPostviewScreen_ResultOhNo2=We are not too impressed with your[CRLF]attempt at that level!
SPostviewScreen_ResultOhNo3=Getting close. You are either pretty[CRLF]good, or simply lucky.
SPostviewScreen_ResultOhNo4=Shame, You were short by a tiny amount.[CRLF]Go for it this time.
SPostviewScreen_ResultOhNo5=Just made it by the skin of your[CRLF]teeth. Time to progress..
SPostviewScreen_ResultOhNo6=More than enough .You have the makings[CRLF]of a master Lemmings player.
SPostviewScreen_ResultOhNo7=What a fine display of Lemmings control.[CRLF]Take a bow then carry on with the game.
SPostviewScreen_ResultOhNo8=WOW! You saved every Lemming.[CRLF]TOTALLY EXCELLENT!
SPostviewScreen_CongratulationOhNo=[CRLF][CRLF]Congratulations![CRLF][CRLF][CRLF][CRLF][CRLF][CRLF]You are truly an Excellent[CRLF]Lemmings player[CRLF][CRLF]The Lemmings Saga continues at a[CRLF]later date, watch this space
